title: A Deep Dive Into Markets, Tesla Earnings Preview
itunes:title: A Deep Dive Into Markets, Tesla Earnings Preview
description:
Hans Olsen, CIO of the Fiduciary Trust Company, discusses market moves and sector trends. Kara Murphy, CIO of Kestra Investment Management, talks markets and gives her investment outlook. RJ Gallo, Senior Portfolio Manager, Fixed Income and Head of the Municipal Bond Group at Federated Hermes, discusses the markets. Esha Dey, Equity Markets Reporter for Bloomberg News, previews Tesla earnings. Hosted by Paul Sweeney and Matt Miller.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
